# Verification artifacts for BRD §3.8 E2E gate

Files under this directory are screenshots, DOM-assertion dumps, or
JSON proof-of-state captured by a Playwright/Puppeteer MCP session
when a feature_list.json entry is being marked `passes: true`.

Naming convention: `<feature_id>.{png,json}` matching the
`verification_artifact_path` field in the entry.

The `hooks/e2e-gate.js` PreToolUse hook refuses any
`passes: false → true` flip unless the artifact at the expected path
exists on disk AND is tracked or staged in git AND is non-empty.

This file is a placeholder so git tracks the empty directory.
